<span id="freeTextContainer9866847846630391291">I&apos;ve said it before but I do not like creepy house stories and I do not like ghost stories. But somehow, I loved this. It was, for the genre, very thriller like. I just kept turning pages faster and faster because I had to know what happened and what the heck was going on. </span>
  <span id="freeText9866847846630391291" style="display:none">I've said it before but I do not like creepy house stories and I do not like ghost stories. But somehow, I loved this. It was, for the genre, very thriller like. I just kept turning pages faster and faster because I had to know what happened and what the heck was going on. </span>
